node.detail_zh: 患者無外遊記錄，7 月 16 日出現症狀。與第 #1368 及 #1400 宗個案有流行病學關連，由檢疫中心送院。
node.detail_en: The patient has no recent travel history and started having symptoms on July 16. Her case is epidemiologically related to the cases of patients #1368 and #1400. She was transferred to hospital from the quarantine centre.
node.classification_zh: 本地個案的密切接觸者
